Quote: (Note: Officer Cadet Training Unit - OCTU - personnel dropped all badges of rank etc. when they went on a course and, in the Middle East at least, wore white puggarees and white taped epaulettes while they were at the School. Hence the nickname `Purity Brigade'.)
